= //<**##683cc4|N/A##** incurs upon proxy SCP-7549 instance, emerging through a doorway connecting a hallway to Recording Station 840-B. **##EC9E69|N/A##** is seated on a metal folding chair, talking into camera.>//


[[span class="bt"]]##EC9E69|N/A:##[[/span]]⠀⠀{{No. I wasn't an only child. My brother was... [http://backrooms-wiki.wikidot.com/ lost]. He was eight, I don't know what happened. He was there... and then he wasn't.}}

= //<Pause.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##EC9E69|N/A:##[[/span]]⠀⠀{{I told myself I was dreaming. In the end, dream or not, it really happened. The multiverse is far larger than anyone of us could have ever known, and it grows, even now. Memorex memories distilled into ones and zeros contain infinite multitudes, only for those who can see the microcosmos contained within the pulses of light. Wouldn't you agree?}}

= //<Pause. Figure turns to look at [[span class="bt"]]##683cc4|N/A##[[/span]].>//

[[span class="bt"]]##683cc4|N/A:##[[/span]]⠀⠀{{How the fuck should I know?}}

= //<Pause.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##EC9E69|N/A:##[[/span]]⠀⠀{{If you don't know, why are you here?}}

= //<Pause.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##683cc4|N/A:##[[/span]]⠀⠀{{Why are any of us here?}}

= //<Long pause.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##EC9E69|N/A:##[[/span]]⠀⠀{{This guy gets it! Anyway-- }}⠀⠀//<Turning back to the camera.>//⠀⠀{{ --what was I saying?}}

= //<Pause.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##683cc4|N/A:##[[/span]]⠀⠀{{...Right.}}

= //<[[span class="bt"]]##683cc4|N/A##[[/span]] turns to leave.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##EC9E69|N/A:##[[/span]]⠀⠀{{I wouldn't wander too far if I were you.}}

= //<Pause.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##683cc4|N/A:##[[/span]]⠀⠀{{Sorry?}}

= //<Pause.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##EC9E69|N/A:##[[/span]]⠀⠀//<Sighs.>//⠀⠀{{Okay. This one will have to be a little light on the intel, sorry about that, future me.}}⠀⠀//<Stops recording.>//⠀⠀{{Think about what's going on here. It might hurt your head, but that's a good indicator of the issue at hand, isn't it?}}

= //<Pause.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##683cc4|N/A:##[[/span]]⠀⠀{{Is it that bad?}}

= //<Pause.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##EC9E69|N/A:##[[/span]]⠀⠀{{Worse.}}⠀⠀//<Pointing to the mass of SCP-7549-1 instances in the room.>//⠀⠀{{There are piles of these tapes just outside the door you came in from. Your mind hasn't seen them, thankfully. Though, we aren't out of the woods yet.}}

= //<One fictive level higher, the Database registers a five percent influx of read-only materia.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##683cc4|N/A:##[[/span]]⠀⠀//<Listening to earpiece.>//⠀⠀{{Was that you?}}

= //<Pause.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##EC9E69|N/A:##[[/span]]⠀⠀{{Afraid not. That was you. Try not to think about the tapes. I've probably said too much already, and you're clearly not trained for this type of complexity.}}

= //<One fictive level higher, the Database registers a seventeen percent influx of read-only materia.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##683cc4|N/A:##[[/span]]⠀⠀//<Listening to earpiece.>//⠀⠀{{What do we do?}}

= //<Pause.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##EC9E69|N/A:##[[/span]]⠀⠀{{Do nothing. Wait to die.}}

= //<One fictive level higher, the Database registers a forty-eight percent influx of read-only materia.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##683cc4|N/A:##[[/span]]⠀⠀//<Listening to earpiece.>//⠀⠀{{I don't understand!}}

= //<Pause.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##EC9E69|N/A:##[[/span]]⠀⠀//<Smiling.>//⠀⠀{{Famous last words.}}

= //<Two fictive levels higher, the Database deletes the narrative containing proxy SCP-7549 instance.>// 

= //<END TRANSCRIPT>//
